      <conclusions>
         <blockContainer class="explanatoryNotes">
            <heading>EXPLANATORY NOTE</heading>
            <block name="comment">(This note is not part of the Order)</block>
            <p>This Order prescribes a rate of 49 pence in the pound as the non-domestic rate to be levied throughout Scotland in respect of the financial year 2019-2020. A rate of 48 pence in the pound was prescribed by the Scottish Ministers as the non-domestic rate to be levied throughout Scotland for the financial year 2018-2019 (<ref eId="c00001" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2018/46">S.S.I. 2018/46</ref>).</p>
